      <h4>The Great Outdoors</h4>

      <p>The outdoors are my home. Whatever the activity might be - from hiking to fishing, or even just stepping out of
        my back door for a breath of fresh air; I always appreciate the feeling of the sun on my face. I've been hiking and
        hunting since I was young and both have given me an extreme love for the land and all creatures who inhabit it. All
        of my best memories are outdoors - including getting the opportunity to meet Steven Pinker at Dream Lake. </p>
      <br />
      <img class="responsive-img" src="/images/pinker.jpg" />

    </div>
