    <div class="section center">
      <h4>Computer Building</h4>
      <p>I think technology in general is insanely cool, so the opportunity to learn and work with state-of-the-art tech
        in your own kitchen is something special. I love working with computers and putting them together, but also learning
        about how the technology itself works. I would love to get into hardware design one day because of this passion.
      </p>
